---
title: Cal Smart Southwest Beyond Meat® Skillet with Charred Corn Wild Rice and Pico de Gallo
description: This glorious Southwest-inspired skillet takes things to the next level with a bed of smoky, charred corn tossed with a wild rice medley and topped with spiced Beyond Meat®. Hot peppers offer a mild heat that's tempered by pico de gallo!

